{
  "message": "test(conformance): add datetime/timedelta adversarial cases (+12)\n\nDatetime adversarial edge cases (12 cases):\n- datetime_nat_arithmetic: NaT propagation in arithmetic\n- timedelta_nat_arithmetic: NaT in timedelta operations\n- datetime_compare_with_nat: comparison behavior with NaT\n- datetime_zero_timedelta: adding zero delta\n- timedelta_negative_large: large negative timedelta\n- datetime_epoch_boundary: Unix epoch handling\n- datetime_year_2038_boundary: Y2038 timestamp handling\n- datetime_leap_second_boundary: leap second edge case\n- busday_empty_holidays: no holidays case\n- busday_all_holidays: all days are holidays\n- timedelta_mul_by_zero: multiplication by zero\n- datetime_sub_same: subtracting identical datetimes\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
